					"type": 23,
					"value": "One-liner for the Civilian5 from the Eastway's Wizards Vignette: a trio of young mages do a Gandalf and put on a light and sound show for passersby on the plaza in front of Sorcerous Sundries. This civilian is named Duddy Dudderken.  \r\n"
